WEBVTT

00:00:28.970 --> 00:00:29.980
That thing...

00:00:31.010 --> 00:00:33.160
comes from the East Sea.

00:00:41.050 --> 00:00:42.810
Come for some sushi.

00:00:44.960 --> 00:00:47.710
- Excuse me, come for some sushi. - What?

00:01:01.410 --> 00:01:04.600
That thing possesses people.

00:01:04.680 --> 00:01:08.730
It penetrates into one's
dark side and weakness...

00:01:08.750 --> 00:01:10.900
and possesses them.

00:01:28.730 --> 00:01:30.360
What is she doing?

00:01:32.170 --> 00:01:35.330
A person who is possessed by that
thing is no longer a human being.

00:01:35.740 --> 00:01:37.979
It enjoys the death of people,

00:01:37.980 --> 00:01:39.900
deceives them,

00:01:40.110 --> 00:01:41.630
and laughs at them.

00:01:44.350 --> 00:01:47.840
Sohn comes from...

00:01:48.650 --> 00:01:50.110
the East Sea.

00:02:01.430 --> 00:02:03.320
I hope this year is better.

00:02:04.070 --> 00:02:06.220
Let's do better this time.

00:02:09.740 --> 00:02:11.660
He has grown up so much.

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:17.670
Hwa Pyung, come over here
and help the elders.

00:02:21.320 --> 00:02:23.270
Hwa Pyung, stop being rude.

00:02:23.290 --> 00:02:25.480
Turn down that TV!

00:02:29.590 --> 00:02:31.150
That woman...

00:02:31.930 --> 00:02:34.420
is staring at me so frighteningly.

00:02:39.400 --> 00:02:41.090
What woman?

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:46.800
That woman hiding behind you.

00:02:47.180 --> 00:02:49.570
That woman who has no hair.

00:02:56.490 --> 00:02:57.910
Are you going to do it again?

00:02:59.060 --> 00:03:01.559
I told you not to say such
things in front of others.

00:03:01.560 --> 00:03:03.299
About 20 years ago,

00:03:03.300 --> 00:03:06.680
an elder's first daughter
died of lung cancer.

00:03:06.770 --> 00:03:09.939
She screamed in pain...

00:03:09.940 --> 00:03:11.820
and caused quite a fuss.

00:03:11.940 --> 00:03:13.830
That's what he saw.

00:03:14.110 --> 00:03:17.139
A psychic has been born from
a hereditary shaman family.

00:03:17.140 --> 00:03:19.160
We need to accept it.

00:03:19.180 --> 00:03:21.800
That's the fate of a psychic.

00:03:21.980 --> 00:03:23.479
Answer me!

00:03:23.480 --> 00:03:25.079
Didn't you hear what Mother just said?

00:03:25.080 --> 00:03:27.710
There's nothing Hwa Pyung can do about it.

00:03:29.150 --> 00:03:30.740
Mom.

00:03:30.760 --> 00:03:32.240
Is there...

00:03:32.490 --> 00:03:34.589
something wrong with me?

00:03:34.590 --> 00:03:36.310
No.

00:03:36.830 --> 00:03:40.550
But if you see something from now on,

00:03:40.570 --> 00:03:43.769
just pretend you don't see
it, and just tell me.

00:03:43.770 --> 00:03:45.220
Okay?

00:03:46.300 --> 00:03:47.760
Okay.

00:03:52.810 --> 00:03:54.700
I don't like that mint-flavored candy.

00:03:54.750 --> 00:03:57.670
Why? This is my favorite candy.

00:04:20.810 --> 00:04:22.909
Why do we worship the wind and rain?

00:04:22.910 --> 00:04:23.979
We pray that we will catch many fishes

00:04:23.980 --> 00:04:25.730
and that ships will avoid accidents.

00:04:25.980 --> 00:04:28.530
- There is another reason too.
- What is it?

00:04:28.750 --> 00:04:30.479
Haven't you heard about the
ghost named Park Il Do?

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:32.170
Park Il Do?

00:04:32.320 --> 00:04:34.410
I heard this when I was a kid.

00:04:35.020 --> 00:04:38.040
A strange man suddenly came to our village.

00:04:38.190 --> 00:04:40.489
He seemed mentally ill.

00:04:40.490 --> 00:04:43.920
After that man came, some people
from the village disappeared.

00:04:44.230 --> 00:04:47.269
Rumors spread that they
were killed by that man.

00:04:47.270 --> 00:04:50.820
But it turned out that he
was possessed by a ghost.

00:04:51.170 --> 00:04:54.109
That ghost said that his name was...

00:04:54.110 --> 00:04:55.469
Park Il Do?

00:04:55.470 --> 00:04:57.560
Yes, Park Il Do.

00:04:57.810 --> 00:04:59.639
The villagers performed an exorcism,

00:04:59.640 --> 00:05:02.249
but failed. They tried to chase him away,

00:05:02.250 --> 00:05:04.019
and that man went wild.

00:05:04.020 --> 00:05:06.019
He stabbed his own eye with a knife...

00:05:06.020 --> 00:05:08.810
and ran into the East Sea.

00:05:09.220 --> 00:05:11.819
He didn't die for days and
floated in the water...

00:05:11.820 --> 00:05:13.580
staring at the villagers.

00:05:14.460 --> 00:05:15.729
Scary, isn't it?

00:05:15.730 --> 00:05:17.999
Since then, people have been
saying, "Park Il Do is coming."

00:05:18.000 --> 00:05:19.420
"Sohn is coming."

00:05:19.700 --> 00:05:21.269
- "Sohn?" - Yes.

00:05:21.270 --> 00:05:23.450
- You know, Sohn means guest... - Hey.

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:27.290
What are you saying to a kid? I
wondered what you were saying.

00:05:28.510 --> 00:05:33.450
The mountain and the wind

00:05:38.220 --> 00:05:40.219
- Yes! - Yes!

00:05:40.220 --> 00:05:44.719
Go to the south of the river

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:51.029
But things go south

00:05:51.030 --> 00:05:55.629
We humans are the rivers

00:05:55.630 --> 00:05:59.799
We humans are the mountains

00:05:59.800 --> 00:06:02.039
- Yes! - Yes!

00:06:02.040 --> 00:06:06.239
The rivers make its bend

00:06:06.240 --> 00:06:10.500
The mountains are too high

00:06:30.030 --> 00:06:34.469
Now we are all gathered here
to pray for our wellbeing.

00:06:34.470 --> 00:06:37.579
Please provide this village
with water and light.

00:06:37.580 --> 00:06:39.609
We wish for a good harvest this year.

00:06:39.610 --> 00:06:42.479
Please fill our boats
up with loads of fish.

00:06:42.480 --> 00:06:44.549
Please bring peace to our
family and children...

00:06:44.550 --> 00:06:46.579
and let us lead a healthy and happy life.

00:06:46.580 --> 00:06:49.489
We pray you will grant
each of our families...

00:06:49.490 --> 00:06:51.559
all our wishes.

00:06:51.560 --> 00:06:53.829
We pray to you.

00:06:53.830 --> 00:06:56.729
Let us plant blue and red
flags on our boats...

00:06:56.730 --> 00:07:00.099
and fill our boats with loads of fish.

00:07:00.100 --> 00:07:02.890
We pray to you.

