00:37:06.300 --> 00:37:07.439
All right.

00:37:07.440 --> 00:37:09.369
It's been three days since Lee Ha Bo...

00:37:09.370 --> 00:37:10.869
went missing.

00:37:10.870 --> 00:37:13.930
Hey, newbie. Did you fill the quota?

00:37:14.010 --> 00:37:15.449
Not yet.

00:37:15.450 --> 00:37:17.209
I'm not a newbie. I'm transferred.

00:37:17.210 --> 00:37:20.719
He's right. You've been driving a taxi...

00:37:20.720 --> 00:37:22.389
in different cities, right?

00:37:22.390 --> 00:37:24.749
Yes, I was looking for someone.

00:37:24.750 --> 00:37:26.580
That's unusual for a young man.

00:37:26.760 --> 00:37:28.759
Are you chased by a loan
shark or something?

00:37:28.760 --> 00:37:30.180
Come on.

00:37:30.730 --> 00:37:33.850
Maybe he's looking for his
lover who ran away from him.

00:37:33.900 --> 00:37:36.950
I'll let you know when I find
your wife who ran away from you.

00:37:37.300 --> 00:37:39.720
Damn. What a funny dude.

00:37:40.570 --> 00:37:42.309
A 40-year-old man surnamed Jeong...

00:37:42.310 --> 00:37:44.639
stabbed and killed staff
of a convenience store...

00:37:44.640 --> 00:37:47.130
with a knife after an argument.

00:37:47.180 --> 00:37:48.800
After committing the crime, he...

00:38:00.520 --> 00:38:02.280
Take us to any motel. Hurry up.

00:38:18.540 --> 00:38:20.560
Darn it.

00:38:34.820 --> 00:38:37.250
Why? What is it?

00:38:39.230 --> 00:38:41.050
She's not your girlfriend, is she?

00:38:43.170 --> 00:38:45.090
It's none of your business.

00:38:45.470 --> 00:38:48.920
You'd better be careful, if you
don't want to be arrested.

00:38:49.670 --> 00:38:50.809
- What? - Her brother...

00:38:50.810 --> 00:38:52.839
is a police officer.

00:38:52.840 --> 00:38:54.460
You didn't know that?

00:39:00.950 --> 00:39:03.189
How do you know that?

00:39:03.190 --> 00:39:04.989
I have psychic ability.

00:39:04.990 --> 00:39:06.559
I'm supposed to have become a shaman,

00:39:06.560 --> 00:39:09.010
but it's a long story.

00:39:10.890 --> 00:39:13.150
You seem to even have a girlfriend...

00:39:13.230 --> 00:39:15.180
who has a temper.

00:39:17.770 --> 00:39:20.569
Let me see. She's got a phone
call from her brother.

00:39:20.570 --> 00:39:22.260
What are you going to do?

00:39:23.240 --> 00:39:24.690
Damn it.

00:39:32.580 --> 00:39:34.449
Yes, I'm a taxi driver.

00:39:34.450 --> 00:39:37.470
Wake up and get out of the car.
You're home.

00:39:37.820 --> 00:39:39.880
Is this your place?

00:39:40.590 --> 00:39:42.459
Who do you think you are?

00:39:42.460 --> 00:39:43.659
- Pardon? - Gosh.

00:39:43.660 --> 00:39:46.899
I wanted to date him and
now you messed it up.

00:39:46.900 --> 00:39:49.520
Hey, I'm not paying for the drive.

00:39:49.830 --> 00:39:51.369
You have to pay.

00:39:51.370 --> 00:39:53.260
Hey, you have to give me money.

00:39:53.600 --> 00:39:55.290
My goodness.

00:39:55.870 --> 00:39:57.430
What a day.

00:40:11.490 --> 00:40:13.919
Hey, sorry I have kept you waiting.

00:40:13.920 --> 00:40:15.580
- It's okay. - Are you sure?

00:40:15.730 --> 00:40:18.389
We have some time. Would you
like to go eat something?

00:40:18.390 --> 00:40:20.299
- How about fried chicken? - Sounds good.

00:40:20.300 --> 00:40:22.920
- Let's go eat fried chicken.
- I can't wait.

00:40:23.130 --> 00:40:26.390
I've always wanted to watch this movie.

00:41:18.790 --> 00:41:20.610
Sorry, I've mistaken you.

00:41:22.760 --> 00:41:26.850
I used to have faith.

00:41:27.530 --> 00:41:30.890
Please give me a dollar
so I can buy alcohol.

00:41:50.650 --> 00:41:53.419
You're one tall man whose eyes are...

00:41:53.420 --> 00:41:55.529
full of sexual energy.

00:41:55.530 --> 00:41:57.329
You'll waste your entire
life as a libertine...

00:41:57.330 --> 00:41:59.099
with alcohol, women, and gambling.

00:41:59.100 --> 00:42:03.150
And when you're old, you'll get
soaked with poop on the street.

00:42:04.030 --> 00:42:05.790
What are you doing?

00:42:07.070 --> 00:42:12.090
Hey, what are you doing at
my workplace at this time?

00:42:18.250 --> 00:42:21.440
Did you hear any news?

00:42:21.750 --> 00:42:24.510
About possessed people?

00:42:24.690 --> 00:42:26.959
Don't talk about scary things at night.

00:42:26.960 --> 00:42:28.710
There's no news.

00:42:29.290 --> 00:42:33.299
Are you here to ask me
that question or to eat?

00:42:33.300 --> 00:42:34.850
Both.

00:42:35.630 --> 00:42:37.629
Haven't you heard anything
from other shamans yet?

00:42:37.630 --> 00:42:39.320
Including churches and Buddhist temples.

00:42:40.370 --> 00:42:44.190
There aren't many people who are
possessed by powerful ghosts.

00:42:46.640 --> 00:42:49.309
Maybe they think that
you're not good anymore.

00:42:49.310 --> 00:42:50.709
That must be why you don't hear anything.

00:42:50.710 --> 00:42:52.130
Hey, you rude brat.

00:42:53.250 --> 00:42:55.300
I'm Yukgwang.

00:42:55.380 --> 00:42:58.070
Six rays of light.

00:42:58.960 --> 00:43:00.519
If you're so frustrated,

00:43:00.520 --> 00:43:03.089
you become a shaman yourself.

00:43:03.090 --> 00:43:04.950
You're possessed too.

00:43:05.830 --> 00:43:08.680
That was a long time ago. I'm not anymore.

00:43:09.830 --> 00:43:11.850
Do you ever call your grandpa?

00:43:12.670 --> 00:43:14.090
Well,

00:43:14.140 --> 00:43:16.060
sometimes.

00:43:16.740 --> 00:43:20.239
What is he called, Priest Choi?
Anyway, stop following him around.

00:43:20.240 --> 00:43:23.179
We can't deal with him.

00:43:23.180 --> 00:43:25.979
Do you even look in the mirror?

00:43:25.980 --> 00:43:28.100
Look what a mess you are.

00:43:28.620 --> 00:43:31.370
How can a young man like you
live like there's no tomorrow?

00:44:10.530 --> 00:44:12.080
Are you here?

00:44:18.230 --> 00:44:20.690
I hated it as a kid,

00:44:22.870 --> 00:44:26.530
but now I wish I could still see spirits.

00:44:29.210 --> 00:44:30.900
Then I could see you, Mom.

00:44:55.400 --> 00:44:57.330
I'll catch him.

00:44:57.710 --> 00:44:59.160
I'll catch him...

00:45:00.280 --> 00:45:01.960
by all means.

00:46:47.080 --> 00:46:48.540
Hey!

00:46:48.650 --> 00:46:50.410
What are you doing there?

00:46:54.690 --> 00:46:56.259
Please call the police.

00:46:56.260 --> 00:46:57.710
What?

00:46:58.130 --> 00:46:59.850
Did you find something there?

00:47:39.170 --> 00:47:41.120
My goodness.

00:47:43.710 --> 00:47:45.439
I was supposed to be on
vacation from tomorrow.

00:47:45.440 --> 00:47:47.679
I promised my daughter I'd
take her to a water park.

00:47:47.680 --> 00:47:49.630
Water park? Forget about it.

00:47:49.750 --> 00:47:53.000
We already had so much to do,
and now we have a murder case?

00:47:57.520 --> 00:47:59.070
Look who's here.

00:47:59.220 --> 00:48:00.710
What is she doing here?

00:48:01.190 --> 00:48:02.740
Kang Gil Young!

00:48:03.830 --> 00:48:05.780
My goodness.

00:48:12.700 --> 00:48:15.560
Is that how you bow to us? Is
your neck stiff or something?

00:48:16.070 --> 00:48:17.560
There's an investigation going on...

00:48:17.740 --> 00:48:19.679
to take disciplinary action against you.

00:48:19.680 --> 00:48:21.939
You should have stayed at the station.

00:48:21.940 --> 00:48:23.970
The result is not out yet.

00:48:27.050 --> 00:48:29.070
Who told her? You?

00:48:29.920 --> 00:48:33.480
How can you eat at the scene?

00:48:34.160 --> 00:48:35.840
You didn't have breakfast, did you?

00:48:36.560 --> 00:48:39.450
- My goodness.
- You need to think before you act.

00:48:40.460 --> 00:48:44.029
The guy you beat up wants to
file a civil suit against you.

00:48:44.030 --> 00:48:45.129
What are you, a gangster?

00:48:45.130 --> 00:48:47.539
He isn't a suspect. He's a criminal.

00:48:47.540 --> 00:48:50.439
Also, he's been convicted of
sexual assault three times.

00:48:50.440 --> 00:48:52.890
- He deserves to be beaten to death.
- Cut it out.

00:48:54.140 --> 00:48:57.370
Send her back. Do as I say.

00:49:03.950 --> 00:49:05.510
Do you have some more?

00:49:10.930 --> 00:49:12.410
Has he been identified?

00:49:12.490 --> 00:49:14.280
The CEO of Shiil Service.

00:49:14.430 --> 00:49:17.420
His ID card, cell phone,
and wallet were all here.

00:49:20.940 --> 00:49:23.486
It seems like he died from excessive
bleeding after being stabbed, right?

00:49:23.510 --> 00:49:25.390
He must have been stabbed
at least 15 times.

00:49:28.980 --> 00:49:30.949
He must have been transferred
here after death, right?

00:49:30.950 --> 00:49:31.979
Yes.

00:49:31.980 --> 00:49:34.540
He must have been killed in a car
before being transferred here.

00:49:34.680 --> 00:49:36.089
The car is nearby.

00:49:36.090 --> 00:49:37.640
It is?

00:49:40.690 --> 00:49:41.889
That's strange.

00:49:41.890 --> 00:49:43.859
Everything about this is strange.

00:49:43.860 --> 00:49:46.920
The drain is completely
dry, but the body is wet.

00:49:46.960 --> 00:49:48.580
Could the water be from the reservoir?

00:49:49.030 --> 00:49:51.050
- Where's the car? - Right over there.

00:49:55.270 --> 00:49:56.760
There it is.

00:50:09.950 --> 00:50:11.919
What a weird punk.

00:50:11.920 --> 00:50:14.180
Who? The killer?

00:50:14.720 --> 00:50:17.910
Why would he leave his car here
and the body in the drain?

00:50:18.030 --> 00:50:20.920
He could have hidden both the car
and the body if he wanted to.

00:50:22.100 --> 00:50:25.190
It looks as if he had a reason
to leave the body in the drain.

00:50:25.700 --> 00:50:27.739
How would we know what
the killer was thinking?

00:50:27.740 --> 00:50:29.790
We're normal people.

00:50:30.970 --> 00:50:33.379
Did you talk to the janitor?

00:50:33.380 --> 00:50:37.030
Yes. But he said he wasn't the
first one to find the body.

00:50:37.310 --> 00:50:38.949
A young man found it first.

00:50:38.950 --> 00:50:41.479
A sly-looking taxi driver,
according to the janitor.

00:50:41.480 --> 00:50:42.789
A taxi driver?

00:50:42.790 --> 00:50:45.670
Hey, stop it!

00:50:46.660 --> 00:50:48.610
What is the taxi driver now?

00:50:57.070 --> 00:50:58.690
Why do you want to know about our CEO?

00:50:59.700 --> 00:51:02.890
He is involved in a criminal case.

00:51:04.110 --> 00:51:06.239
Do you clean drains too?

00:51:06.240 --> 00:51:07.240
We do.

00:51:07.241 --> 00:51:10.349
Have you ever cleaned the
drains of Nakmak Reservoir?

00:51:10.350 --> 00:51:15.440
Well... It was a couple of months ago.

00:51:15.680 --> 00:51:17.810
Something happened, right?

00:51:18.320 --> 00:51:20.919
One of our employees got hurt.

00:51:20.920 --> 00:51:22.340
Hurt?

00:51:24.760 --> 00:51:27.780
Cleaning drains is a pretty dangerous job.

00:51:28.230 --> 00:51:29.920
Our client was...

00:51:30.100 --> 00:51:31.790
pushing us,

00:51:32.170 --> 00:51:33.720
so our employee got seriously injured.

00:51:34.500 --> 00:51:37.960
Did that make him fall out with the CEO?

00:51:39.840 --> 00:51:41.760
He was just a temporary worker.

00:51:41.810 --> 00:51:44.430
If our client keeps pushing us,

00:51:44.810 --> 00:51:47.200
what can we do?

00:51:47.950 --> 00:51:50.840
Many people seem to want to
know about that incident today.

00:51:51.950 --> 00:51:53.119
Was someone else here?

00:51:53.120 --> 00:51:54.889
A taxi driver came...

00:51:54.890 --> 00:51:56.959
and asked for Kim Young Soo's phone number.

00:51:56.960 --> 00:51:59.080
Did he look sly by any chance?

00:52:00.530 --> 00:52:02.280
Thank you.

00:52:02.530 --> 00:52:05.399
By the way, where are you from again?

00:52:05.400 --> 00:52:07.560
Well...

00:52:07.770 --> 00:52:10.709
Our organization was founded recently.

00:52:10.710 --> 00:52:12.209
We're looking into cases...

00:52:12.210 --> 00:52:15.430
where workers were treated unfairly.

00:52:18.180 --> 00:52:20.670
He had a choking accident in the drain,

00:52:21.220 --> 00:52:23.249
which resulted in brain damage.

00:52:23.250 --> 00:52:27.410
He can't walk or speak properly anymore.

00:52:33.030 --> 00:52:35.120
It was raining so hard,

00:52:35.800 --> 00:52:38.520
and they forced him to clean the drain.

00:52:39.870 --> 00:52:42.620
The CEO refuses to take responsibility.

00:52:43.570 --> 00:52:46.069
They say a temporary worker is not
entitled to any compensation.

00:52:46.070 --> 00:52:49.030
The big company that gave them
the work is just sitting back.

00:52:49.910 --> 00:52:52.470
They put all the blame on my husband.

00:52:55.280 --> 00:52:56.940
That's terrible.

00:52:58.320 --> 00:53:00.510
If I may,

00:53:00.620 --> 00:53:04.380
I'd like to talk to your
husband for a moment.

00:53:05.590 --> 00:53:07.080
Sure.

00:53:13.270 --> 00:53:15.120
Hello, sir.

00:53:15.400 --> 00:53:17.609
I have some questions for you.

00:53:17.610 --> 00:53:19.590
Do you understand what I say?

00:53:23.980 --> 00:53:25.500
Well...

00:53:28.180 --> 00:53:29.640
Have you ever...

00:53:29.820 --> 00:53:32.910
seen this man by any chance?

00:53:33.120 --> 00:53:35.140
Who is he?

00:53:36.120 --> 00:53:39.050
Has he ever been here?

00:53:47.300 --> 00:53:49.190
Honey.

00:53:49.670 --> 00:53:51.460
What's wrong?

00:53:52.610 --> 00:53:54.100
Honey.

00:53:58.310 --> 00:54:00.370
Please go back now.

00:54:01.950 --> 00:54:05.219
If your husband starts to act strangely,

00:54:05.220 --> 00:54:07.880
please contact me, okay?

00:54:08.520 --> 00:54:10.289
Here's my number.

00:54:10.290 --> 00:54:12.580
Sorry? What do you mean?

00:54:14.460 --> 00:54:16.569
He might start to act
like a different person.

00:54:16.570 --> 00:54:18.629
Then you need to call
me as soon as possible.

00:54:18.630 --> 00:54:20.399
I don't care if you call me at night.

00:54:20.400 --> 00:54:22.060
Do you understand?

00:54:22.700 --> 00:54:24.160
Okay.

00:54:25.570 --> 00:54:27.030
Bye.

00:54:31.950 --> 00:54:34.300
Who are you?

00:54:36.820 --> 00:54:40.189
Well, I just talked to your parents.

00:54:40.190 --> 00:54:41.640
I'm from a social organization.

00:54:49.530 --> 00:54:51.020
Aren't you going in?

00:54:52.470 --> 00:54:54.669
I have to eat and go to a private class,

00:54:54.670 --> 00:54:56.590
but I don't want to go in.

00:54:57.440 --> 00:54:58.860
Why not?

00:54:59.010 --> 00:55:01.230
Are you scared of your dad or something?

00:55:02.480 --> 00:55:04.049
How did you know?

00:55:04.050 --> 00:55:06.530
I know these things well.

00:55:06.650 --> 00:55:09.900
Don't worry too much. He'll get better.

00:55:11.790 --> 00:55:13.780
But his brain is damaged.

00:55:14.690 --> 00:55:18.510
He's not likely to recover.
I know that much.

00:55:21.500 --> 00:55:24.450
- You may be right. - But...

00:55:25.200 --> 00:55:29.060
regardless of his injury, he's
been a little weird lately.

00:55:30.440 --> 00:55:31.990
What do you mean?

00:55:32.340 --> 00:55:36.000
He's like a different person.

00:55:38.080 --> 00:55:40.030
Did you see anything?

00:55:40.680 --> 00:55:42.300
I have to go to a lesson.

00:55:43.150 --> 00:55:46.819
Oh, I'm sorry. You said you need to eat.

00:55:46.820 --> 00:55:49.410
Here. Get something on your way.

00:55:49.830 --> 00:55:51.280
I can't take it.

00:55:52.060 --> 00:55:53.820
I'll get in trouble.

00:56:11.780 --> 00:56:14.240
Gosh. What is it?

00:56:15.550 --> 00:56:17.149
I can't give you a ride.
I'm taking a break.

00:56:17.150 --> 00:56:19.919
I'm from the police. Please step out.

00:56:19.920 --> 00:56:21.380
Why?

00:56:21.460 --> 00:56:24.610
Am I not supposed to park here?

00:56:25.590 --> 00:56:28.599
On TV, the police always
show their ID cards.

00:56:28.600 --> 00:56:30.150
Are you really from the police?

00:56:34.900 --> 00:56:37.230
You were at Nakmak Reservoir
this morning, weren't you?

00:56:38.140 --> 00:56:39.590
Was I?

00:56:40.480 --> 00:56:43.400
Well, a taxi goes everywhere.

00:56:43.980 --> 00:56:46.300
I have a reservation. Can I go now?

00:56:47.780 --> 00:56:50.219
Your hand. You could have hurt yourself.

00:56:50.220 --> 00:56:51.619
You have a wrong person.

00:56:51.620 --> 00:56:53.759
You got caught on security cameras
around Nakmak Reservoir...

00:56:53.760 --> 00:56:56.880
and at Shiil Service.

00:56:56.960 --> 00:56:58.480
It's you.

00:57:02.160 --> 00:57:03.650
Gosh.

00:57:07.740 --> 00:57:09.860
You have no criminal record.

00:57:11.340 --> 00:57:14.760
Yun Hwa Pyung, what were
you doing there so early?

00:57:15.140 --> 00:57:17.900
I was just passing by. I'm
a taxi driver, you know.

00:57:18.010 --> 00:57:20.170
It's a remote place.

00:57:20.650 --> 00:57:22.549
I had to pee. Fine, I peed on the street.

00:57:22.550 --> 00:57:24.170
Please forgive me this once.

00:57:25.390 --> 00:57:28.059
Were you just passing by the
victim's former office too?

00:57:28.060 --> 00:57:30.510
Yes. What's with this guy?

00:57:30.560 --> 00:57:33.580
His face is a mess.

00:57:40.040 --> 00:57:42.339
You beat him up?

00:57:42.340 --> 00:57:45.639
Can you still do that these days?

00:57:45.640 --> 00:57:48.279
Hey. You want me to beat you up too?

00:57:48.280 --> 00:57:49.779
Answer my questions.

00:57:49.780 --> 00:57:51.749
You said I was just a witness.

00:57:51.750 --> 00:57:53.349
Gosh, are you allowed to do this?

00:57:53.350 --> 00:57:57.049
If you keep this up, I will
have you arrested as a suspect.

00:57:57.050 --> 00:57:59.819
- Why? - Don't you think it's suspicious?

00:57:59.820 --> 00:58:01.240
What you've done.

00:58:02.360 --> 00:58:05.450
- You want me to tell you the truth? - Yes.

00:58:08.730 --> 00:58:10.180
Well...

00:58:10.430 --> 00:58:13.120
It'll probably sound strange.

00:58:13.640 --> 00:58:17.130
I have this special ability.

00:58:17.140 --> 00:58:19.069
What should I say?

00:58:19.070 --> 00:58:22.130
I see things.

00:58:23.250 --> 00:58:25.300
It started when I was little.

00:58:25.510 --> 00:58:27.619
Last night,

00:58:27.620 --> 00:58:30.740
I suddenly saw the killer
leave the body in the drain.

00:58:32.620 --> 00:58:34.040
Are you kidding me?

00:58:36.460 --> 00:58:38.210
I knew you wouldn't believe it.

00:58:38.490 --> 00:58:41.680
Hey, the first identification
result is out. Let's go.

00:58:42.030 --> 00:58:43.550
Hold on.

00:58:43.730 --> 00:58:45.629
What about me? I have an emergency.

00:58:45.630 --> 00:58:48.560
- What emergency?
- You won't believe me anyway.

00:58:48.600 --> 00:58:50.460
Wait here.

00:58:52.840 --> 00:58:55.530
Gosh. I really have an emergency.

00:58:57.950 --> 00:59:00.749
He's the taxi driver, right?
Wrap it up and send him back.

00:59:00.750 --> 00:59:02.449
He's really suspicious.

00:59:02.450 --> 00:59:03.819
He visited both the victim's workplace...

00:59:03.820 --> 00:59:06.819
and the injured employee's home.

00:59:06.820 --> 00:59:09.489
Why would he? That's really strange.

00:59:09.490 --> 00:59:11.129
Did they find anything on the body?

00:59:11.130 --> 00:59:12.689
Salt.

00:59:12.690 --> 00:59:14.399
The body was soaked in seawater.

00:59:14.400 --> 00:59:15.729
Isn't that weird?

00:59:15.730 --> 00:59:18.320
Was there seawater in
the drain or something?

00:59:18.630 --> 00:59:21.199
There are 14 stab wounds.

00:59:21.200 --> 00:59:23.809
And they're all in random places.
What a crazy jerk.

00:59:23.810 --> 00:59:26.439
Either he's crazy or it was resentment.

00:59:26.440 --> 00:59:30.160
I think I should go back to
the injured employee's home.

00:59:30.380 --> 00:59:33.740
You said he couldn't
walk or speak properly.

00:59:33.780 --> 00:59:36.889
The killer left the body
in the drain on purpose.

00:59:36.890 --> 00:59:39.410
I think it has something
to do with that family.

00:59:40.560 --> 00:59:42.019
Also, those white sneakers...

00:59:42.020 --> 00:59:43.540
White sneakers?

00:59:48.300 --> 00:59:50.020
I'm going to work.

00:59:57.970 --> 00:59:59.860
What happened to these?

01:00:01.140 --> 01:00:02.660
Water.

01:00:04.610 --> 01:00:06.070
Water.

01:00:07.920 --> 01:00:10.410
Why are you so thirsty these days?

01:00:10.890 --> 01:00:12.749
I won't be back until morning.

01:00:12.750 --> 01:00:14.180
Water.

01:00:15.890 --> 01:00:18.580
- All of it. - What?

01:00:24.330 --> 01:00:27.490
Slow down. Hold on.

01:00:29.100 --> 01:00:32.009
You have wounds on your hands.

01:00:32.010 --> 01:00:33.269
What happened?

01:00:33.270 --> 01:00:35.130
Let's all die.

01:00:36.080 --> 01:00:37.879
Let's all die.

01:00:37.880 --> 01:00:39.300
Honey.

01:00:39.710 --> 01:00:41.640
What's with you?

01:00:42.820 --> 01:00:46.540
What happened to your hands?

01:00:51.090 --> 01:00:53.310
Let's all die.

01:01:03.540 --> 01:01:05.030
Honey.

01:01:06.370 --> 01:01:09.500
I'm going to work.

01:01:28.730 --> 01:01:30.220
What?

01:01:30.800 --> 01:01:33.050
Are you going to call that guy?

01:01:47.920 --> 01:01:49.440
Honey.

01:01:50.550 --> 01:01:52.040
You can speak...

01:03:12.430 --> 01:03:16.369
You look comfortable as if you're at home.

01:03:16.370 --> 01:03:17.990
You must have been here a lot.

01:03:18.440 --> 01:03:19.930
You can go now.

01:03:19.970 --> 01:03:22.730
We checked your dashcam and
found nothing suspicious.

01:03:25.350 --> 01:03:27.670
Hey. Say bye at least.

01:03:54.680 --> 01:03:56.900
Hey. What are you doing here?

01:03:56.950 --> 01:03:58.500
Why are you back?

01:03:58.780 --> 01:04:00.270
What is it?

01:04:02.680 --> 01:04:04.110
Hey!

01:05:02.510 --> 01:05:04.170
The body is wet again.

01:05:16.260 --> 01:05:18.180
Hey. What are you doing?

01:05:19.530 --> 01:05:21.529
Neither her husband nor
her daughter is here.

01:05:21.530 --> 01:05:22.980
Her daughter?

01:05:27.100 --> 01:05:30.220
I get it, so leave the scene. Right now.

01:05:31.010 --> 01:05:33.209
- Get out. - Fine.

01:05:33.210 --> 01:05:35.530
I get it, okay?

01:05:59.200 --> 01:06:00.720
What's that?

01:06:22.860 --> 01:06:24.929
I think the daughter is alive.

01:06:24.930 --> 01:06:27.799
Someone's life is on the line.
We have to do something.

01:06:27.800 --> 01:06:29.859
We need to make sure if
he is possessed first.

01:06:29.860 --> 01:06:31.199
We shouldn't rush.

01:06:31.200 --> 01:06:32.499
I think it's more dangerous for you.

01:06:32.500 --> 01:06:34.199
You seem to be possessed already.

01:06:34.200 --> 01:06:36.460
- Where is he? He's in there, right?
- Hold on.

01:06:37.140 --> 01:06:39.809
He's going to perform an exorcism?

01:06:39.810 --> 01:06:41.739
He's a taxi driver.

01:06:41.740 --> 01:06:43.879
We're dealing with something too dangerous.

01:06:43.880 --> 01:06:45.979
Are you possessed or something?

01:06:45.980 --> 01:06:47.719
Where is your daughter right now?

01:06:47.720 --> 01:06:49.900
Where is she? Tell me!